Executive Profile
Robert D. Perlmutter  Chief Operating Officer and Senior Executive Vice President, The Macerich CompanyAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships55$3,400,662As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Robert D. Perlmutter, also known as Bobby, has been an Chief Operating Officer and Senior Executive Vice President at The Macerich Company since February 12,  2016. Mr. Perlmutter served as a Managing Member of Davis Street Land Company, LLC. He served as an Executive Vice President of Leasing at The Macerich Company since April 19, 2012 until February 12,  2016. He served as the President and Chief Executive Officer at Heitman Retail Properties, a subsidiary of ... Heitman Properties, Ltd. from 1990 to 1998. From 1988 to 1990, he served as Heitman Financial's President, a capacity in which he was responsible for overseeing all of its acquisitions, financings and dispositions. From 1983 to 1988, he worked as an Investment Analyst for Heitman Financial Services, Ltd. in its acquisitions and dispositions division. He serves as Managing Member of Davis Street Land Company, LLC. He has been a Trustee of Chatham Lodging Trust since April 2010. He served as a Director of Prime Retail Inc. from 1998 to 2001 and Horizon Group Inc. since 1997. He serves as a Member of the International Council of Shopping Centers ("ICSC"), the Illinois ICSC Committee and NAREIT. He is a Member of First Bank of Highland Park. Mr. Perlmutter holds a Bachelor of Science degree in Business Administration (BSBA) and Real Estate from the University of Colorado in Boulder.Read Full Background




