Insider Activity


Individual




Robert D. Perlmutter



Mr. Robert D. Perlmutter is Chief Operating Officer & Senior Executive VP at Macerich Co., Independent Trustee at Chatham Lodging Trust and a Member at International Council of Shopping Centers, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Chatham Lodging Trust and First Bank of Highland Park. Mr. Perlmutter was previously employed as Managing Member by Davis Street Land Co. LLC, Chief Executive Officer by Heitman Properties, and President by Heitman Financial Services LLC. He also served on the board at Prime Retail, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from The University of Colorado.



