Donate to Hassenfeld Children’s Hospital





 
 
 
 
 


 




 
 
 
 





 













Help Us Provide the Finest Care for Kids

        DONATE NOW
      




  What sets us apart


  At Hassenfeld Children’s Hospital, we ensure that every child gets the best medical care possible.







        Our 400+ physicians are experts in over 30 specialties. 
      







        We are advancing integrative medicine by providing children and families stress-relieving support such as yoga, massage, and meditation.
      







        We are the future of research and education, studying a range of pediatric diseases.
      





Donate to Hassenfeld Children’s Hospital


When your child is sick, you want the best care possible.


 At Hassenfeld Children’s Hospital at NYU Langone, we know this — and we understand that caring for infants, children, and teenagers is a special privilege. That’s why we partner with children and their families to deliver expert medical and surgical care.
  

  Our talented team of doctors, nurses, child life specialists, social workers, and other medical professionals — are all committed to providing personalized, compassionate care that addresses the needs of the entire family.


And we will be there for your family too — should you ever need us.




















