About
Dr. Robert Perlmutter, MD is a Doctor primarily located in West Hills, CA. He has 51 years of experience. His specialties include General Practice and Family Medicine.                    Dr. Perlmutter is affiliated with                            Northridge Hospital Medical Center,                            Encino-Tarzana Regional Medical Center-Encino Campus and                            Valley Presbyterian Hospital.
                 He speaks English.



